  "key_design_notes": [
    "DownloadManager is the facade: routes download/install/update/remove/cleanup to the correct DownloaderInterface by type string key",
    "Two main downloader hierarchies: FileDownloader (dist/archive) and VcsDownloader (source/VCS)",
    "ArchiveDownloader adds archive-extraction logic on top of FileDownloader; subclasses only implement extract()",
    "VcsDownloader implements the template-method pattern: public download/install/update delegate to abstract doDownload/doInstall/doUpdate",
    "PathDownloader handles local path installs via symlink or mirror-copy strategies (not VCS, not archive)",
    "GitDownloader adds caching (cache-vcs-dir), stash/discard interactive prompt, unpushed-changes detection",
    "All operations return React\\Promise\\PromiseInterface for async/parallel execution",
    "DownloadManager.download() includes source/dist fallback logic with retry on RuntimeException",
    "getInstallationSource() returns 'dist' for FileDownloader hierarchy, 'source' for VcsDownloader hierarchy",
    "ChangeReportInterface: getLocalChanges() — implemented by FileDownloader (Comparer diff) and all VcsDownloaders",
    "DvcsDownloaderInterface: getUnpushedChanges() — implemented only by GitDownloader"
  ],

